description:
How triggered are you?

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This is it. The point of no return. I've said "the chains are off" time and time again now, but never has it had such profound significance until the release of this video. Because today, the YouTube channel once known as "EmperorLemon" has entered a new age. Gone are the days of only happy-go-lucky YTPs. I have crossed over to the rant side of YouTube, and this channel will never, Never, EEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEVER be the same, a-gain.

I don't know what exactly lies ahead for the future of this channel, and I understand that not all of you will be content with my content. For those of you who stick with me, I express my total gratitude. I mentioned a few months ago that 18 is a year of change. It just so happens that six years of producing the same YouTube videos makes Emp a dull boy... err rather gets kind of stale. I've reached a stage in my life where I am excited to try new things. The video you see before you could be the beginning of an unprecedented era of success for my channel. It could also be the beginning of the downfall of my entire livelihood. I am willing to accept either of these consequences as long as I earn the satisfaction of exploring new frontiers.  There is one thing, however, that has not changed.

It's never ogre.

Music:
Franz Liszt - Hungarian Rhapsody No.2 (Orchestra version)
The Sound of Silence: Arrested Development Mariachi Band Version
Evanescence - Bring Me To Life
Everyday - Carly Comando
